attributionInfo.brokerName: Blue Skies R E & Resort Rental

data.description: Come See this BEAUTIFUL 2-Story Home in the woods! Do you want a second home, rental or weekend escape or maybe a 1031 Exchange? This wonderful 2BD, 1.5BA 1460 SQ FT Home has it all. The Streets are maintained by the County in the winter. Gambrel Roof Design gives this home the typical "Cabin" feeling. The front yard is enclosed with a chain link fence with a gate that opens to a Parking area. There is a front porch to hang out on, have a cup of coffee or afternoon cocktail. Inside feels warm and cozy and inviting with BEAR THEMED decorations throughout, Wood lined walls and ceilings, a nice layout, and 2 Brick Fireplaces, (Living Room and Primary Bedroom). The Bedrooms are upstairs and have balconies off each room, overlooking the front and back areas. The Living Room and Kitchen are downstairs and there is a Bonus Room off the kitchen that is currently used as a Game Room / Entertainment hangout. There have been lots of upgrades made to the home to include New HAMPSTEAD Water resistant Wood based Vinyl Flooring, New toilets, New Countertops, Sinks, Towel racks and Faucets in both Bathrooms, New Vanity in Downstairs Bathroom, New Hot Water Heater and New Stackable Washer and Dryer, stainless steel appliances in the Kitchen, custom wood gates separating side yards from back yard, a Storage Shed and Recent tree trimming and tree removal. Pull up a chair and enjoy the fenced backyard or have a BBQ with friends surrounded by Pines. Located in the Erwin Lake area, the home is close to local ski resorts, shopping, restaurants and bars and sits in between BARK PARK Dog Park and Erwin Lake Park. This is a great location with a lot to explore nearby.
